text.textblock: In notice document 89-27715 beginning on page 48817 in the issue of Monday, November 27, 1989, make the following correction:
On page 48817, in the last line of the third column, the word southeast is hereby corrected to read northwest.
For a period of 45 days from publication, interested parties may submit comments to the District Manager, c/o Area Manager, Folsom Resource Area, Folsom, CA 95630
